    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那这个状态机的入口是idle状态吗？用户从物流仓库进入后先处于空闲状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "idle"
